name: Wedding present :: COMMISSION US
description:
Rob & Steph. Commissioned Wedding present. 

Hand painted box with individual illustrations wrapped inside and bound with an appropriate 'tying the' knot! Each illustration depicts something that they 'love' including each other. NOT FOR SALE

Do you have an idea or maybe NO idea for any excuse for a gift and see what we come up with! Send an email to :: info@suki-design.com

name: Invitations :: COMMISSION US
description:
Commission original illustrations from photos or sourced imagery. Patterns, photography, typography can all feature. Suki will also source print costs and provide paper samples and finishes to help you decide on exactly what you want!

Contact info@suki-design.com for estimates

name: Vintage Bottles BLUE :: FOR HIRE
description:
For hire as props, table centres (vases), display. Drape with flowers, feathers, ribbons or beads. 

Their original uses were as ink bottles, perfume, milk, ginger beer, wine, table sauces and medicine.

They were found in Teddington, Middlesex, UK and age from mid 1800's-mid 1900's.

They have been categorised by style/size or colour but mismatched work well together too. Some are ceramic. 

Not all bottles have been photographed because there are about 200 in total but do contact me for further information and prices (From £1 a bottle) at info@suki-design.com and I will get straight back to you.
